room_title: Escape room "Cold Case 146" by Escape Oshkosh in Oshkosh
room_address: 146 Algoma Blvd Suite C Oshkosh, WI 54901
room_description: You are a team of private investigators, hired by the Hall family to look into the disappearance of their daughter, who went missing over three years ago. Your team has been hired to investigate the primary suspect, Dr. Simon Jenkins. Can you discover what he is hiding and bring some closure to the Hall family?
